name: Reverse the array
instruction:
The `reverseArray` function takes an array that may contain different data types.

The function should return a new array with the elements in reverse order.

Example function calls:
```javascript
reverseArray([1, 2, 3]) // [3, 2, 1]
reverseArray(["hello" , 12, "world", 234, false]) // [false, 234, "world", 12, "hello"]
```
